text:
Oh, thank you!
This is exactly what I needed.

Haha~, great~
...Is that, are you ego surfing~?

Yes, it is. The magazine we talked about the other
day is out today, so do you want me to grab one for you?

Oh, really!?
That'd be great! Thanks.

Both of you, want to come with me?
I found something interesting outside!

Oh! What is it? I'm in!
You sure you don't need someone else?

Haha, it's not that big of a deal.
Anyway, how was the ego surfing? Any good comments?

Yeah, there were some.
But it's not good to just read the positive ones, you know.

─ Anyway,
aren't you thirsty from running around? Need some tea?
No, no! I'll go get it myself, it's okay...
─Sorry, can you get me one, please?
